Include-Package

This package aims to make packages of perl modules easily loaded and run (with
versioning options etc)

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Include::Package

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Include-Package

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Include-Package

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Include-Package

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Include-Package/

    Source Code
        git://github.com/ivanwills/Include-Package.git

